schools.name: Rim Of The World Senior High School

data.description: This home recently appraised for $415k have your agent call today to possibly get closing cost for you! Mountain living at its best. This home has so much potential located a short 3-minute drive to Lake Gregory or 15-minute walk if you want to get that cardio in! Close to market, local shops and dining. 2 bedrooms and 1 bath located on main floor. Downstairs you have another restroom and bedroom with laundry area and a unfinished basement area. Think of the potential to rent out lower floor for rental income! while having separate entrances for privacy. Home is located on a very private road with plenty of parking offering 3-4 spaces to park which is nice for a mountain home.
